  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libdbusmenu-lxqt</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libdbusmenu-lxqt</application> package provides a
      Qt implementation of the DBusMenu protocol.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

